, Purdue\'s Discovery Park is home to researchers and students alike, from fields including electrical engineering, computer science, biology, economics, management, and the liberal arts. The park offers an environment where projects can flourish in a setting that fosters collaborative research. Discovery Park aims to link Purdue University more closely with the Indiana and U.S. economies, further strengthening and defining those relationships in an endeavor to create a combinational power greater than any individual strength.\"><photo name=\"Discovery Park\" caption=\"Birck Nanotechnology Center\" location=\"tour/discoverypark/2.jpg\" /><photo name=\"Discovery Park\" caption=\"Burton D. Morgan Center for Entrepreneurship\" location=\"tour/discoverypark/3.jpg\" /><pano lat=\"40.42371441938235\" lng=\"-86.92330241203308\" pov=\"135\" icon=\"tour/discoverypark/360.jpg\" /></marker><marker name=\"Doyle Laboratory\" abbreviation=\"DOYL\" lat=\"40.418715698627444\" lng=\"-86.91551327705383\" image=\"tour/P.jpg\" streetaddress=\"404 S. University Street\" citystatezip=\"West Lafayette, IN 47907\" phone=\"\" virtualtour=\"\" webpage=\"\" category=\"acad\" tourcategory=\"\" icontype=\"acad\" details=\"\" /><marker name=\"Drug Discovery\" abbreviation=\"DRUG\" lat=\"40.421708\" lng=\"-86.917279\" image=\"tour/P.jpg\" streetaddress=\"720 Clinic Dr.\" citystatezip=\"West Lafayette, IN 47907\" phone=\"\" virtualtour=\"\" webpage=\"\" category=\"acad\" tourcategory=\"\" icontype=\"acad\" details=\"\" /><marker name=\"Electrical Engineering Building\" abbreviation=\"EE\" lat=\"40.428844\" lng=\"-86.911758\" image=\"tour/P.jpg\" streetaddress=\"465 Northwestern Avenue\" citystatezip=\"West Lafayette, IN 47907\" phone=\"\" virtualtour=\"\" webpage=\"\" category=\"acad\" tourcategory=\"Historic\" icontype=\"acad\" details=\"\" /><marker name=\"Elliott Hall of Music\" abbreviation=\"ELLT\" lat=\"40.427828\" lng=\"-86.915081\" image=\"graphics/mapphotos/elliott.jpg\" streetaddress=\"7